1
00:00:21,400 --> 00:00:21,760
Roman

2
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:27,360
What do you want to know?

3
00:00:27,560 --> 00:00:28,360
The truth

4
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:29,960
Are you sure?

5
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:32,320
Yes, that's why I've come to you

6
00:00:43,240 --> 00:00:46,040
How many women have you had
in your life?

7
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:49,000
You know, women, girls or
whatever you call them

8
00:00:51,880 --> 00:00:54,000
Eight... nine...
I don't know, maybe fifteen

9
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:55,160
That's enough

10
00:00:56,160 --> 00:00:58,200
I've been married for ten years now
And frankly...

11
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,520
That's enough, too

12
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:04,640
Are you sure I don't ever be able to
make love to any woman?

13
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:08,120
I'm afraid you won't, the findings are
typical, and so are the symptoms

14
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,280
What's your wife like?

15
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:31,280
She's wonderful

16
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:35,680
Take a divorce

17
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:06,800
Romek

18
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,440
I heard your car

19
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,440
Come on

20
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:41,000
You didn't want to meet you,
did you?

21
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:42,800
I did

22
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:47,600
Your suit is dripping wet

23
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,960
Don't you want to know
why I went to Krakow?

24
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,480
Why, you have friends there

25
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,320
Just one

26
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:31,840
Why don't you tell me about Zagreb?

27
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:39,200
I delivered several lectures
I assisted during several operations

28
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:43,360
On three occasions, I operated myself
I got paid and by the tim

29
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:47,680
I was leaving, the money I got was only
worth a half of its original value

30
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,480
Are you tired?

31
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:53,840
No

32
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,560
I say, Hanka darling...

33
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:04,800
Mhm... Not now, please

34
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,560
Tell me everything

35
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:42,640
I'm not afraid anymore

36
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,320
I went to Krakow to meet Mikolaj

37
00:06:57,840 --> 00:07:01,160
He's a friend of mine
I told you about him once, didn't I?

38
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:02,920
That son of a bitch, I remember

39
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:06,400
Well, he examined me and
had all the analyses made

40
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,480
He was quite frank

41
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:14,080
I haven't any chances
Today, tomorrow...

42
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,160
Or ever...

43
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,160
I don't believe it

44
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,200
These are facts

45
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:25,800
Do you love me?

46
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,280
Well, do you or not?

47
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:49,400
You're afraid to say you do
although you do love me after all

48
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:53,480
Love is not just panting in bed
for five minutes once a week

49
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:56,520
It is that, too

50
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:58,240
It's just biology

51
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:04,000
True love is situated in one's heart
and not between the legs

52
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:21,120
What matters to me is what we have
and not what we haven't

53
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,160
You're young and...

54
00:08:25,280 --> 00:08:26,400
I can manage

55
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,560
You'll have to find yourself a lover

56
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,800
That is, if you haven't found one yet

57
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:42,480
I haven't

58
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:48,240
Some things are better left unsaid

59
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,360
Oh no

60
00:08:56,960 --> 00:09:01,640
All right, so you've been frank with me
You won't ever be able to make love to me

61
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:05,520
At least that's what the doctors say
I'm telling you this

62
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:10,720
I want to be with you anyway

63
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:14,120
I love you

64
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,120
May I cuddle up to you?

65
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:21,840
Yes

66
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,720
Tightly, O.K.?

67
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:55,680
You asleep, Hanka?

68
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:00,960
No

69
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:06,440
We've never wanted a baby

70
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,760
No

71
