Can I help?

74
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:30,320
If you're so kind...
Just hold the funnel, will you?

75
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,160
May I join, Doctor?

76
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,160
Make a decision

77
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:46,640
It's not very good for you

78
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,680
