79
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:51,840
The ward head told me he found it rather
difficult to come to terms with you

80
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,800
Really? But it's perfectly simple

81
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:57,680
You see, Doctor

82
00:12:01,280 --> 00:12:03,040
I have a voice

83
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:04,160
How's that?

84
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:05,240
A singing voice

85
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:08,840
My mother is a hard-working woman
She wants me to be somebody

86
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:13,680
I wasn't admitted to the school
of music because of my heart

87
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:15,920
I shouldn't sing, my heart's too weak,
but Mother wants me to become a singer

88
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,760
What's your specialty?

89
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,680
Bach and Mahler
Do you know Mahler?

90
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:22,720
And... van den Budemayer?

91
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,480
