92
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:27,400
His works are... well, difficult
But I can sing them

93
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:31,840
Mother wants me to make a career
abroad or at least here

94
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:34,120
This is what that operation's for

95
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:38,720
