on me or better still, you

96
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:42,600
Do you want it, too?

97
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:49,280
I want to live, that's enough for me
I don't have to sing

98
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:51,520
Besides, I'm scared

99
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:54,240
I guess the ward head wanted you to

100
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:56,200
reassure me to tell me
it isn't dangerous

101
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:58,200
I'll be able to do everything
afterwards...

102
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:00,480
Well, go on, tell me

103
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:02,800
Know what, it's not that simple

104
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:05,840
Such operations are usually
carried out to save, I mean...

105
00:13:06,280 --> 00:13:10,320
They are the last resort,
when nothing else can be done

106
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:12,640
Which is not the case with me, right?

107
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:16,040
Frankly speaking, that's what I mean

108
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,760
Various people have different needs

109
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:22,880
Mother wants me to have everything

110
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:26,640
...while I only need this much

111
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,840
Good afternoon
May I speak to Hanka please?

112
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,480
