113
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:19,440
Oh, I thought she was
Thank you

114
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:20,480
Want me to give her a message?

115
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:22,320
No, thanks
I'll try to reach her later

116
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:57,720
