You didn't come at four

128
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,520
All right

129
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:29,280
Hanka darling

130
00:16:35,160 --> 00:16:36,960
All right, I'll be there

131
00:16:39,400 --> 00:16:40,560
Yes, it's better this way

132
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:42,800
