Never call me on the phone at home

172
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:26,960
unless you have to

173
00:27:27,360 --> 00:27:28,000
Anything wrong?

174
00:27:28,520 --> 00:27:30,760
No, phone me at the office,
it's better that way

175
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:32,360
Ten to six, right?

176
00:27:32,520 --> 00:27:35,080
And ten to eight
on Thursdays and Tuesdays

177
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:37,360
As you wish, Madam
Have you been to your mother's flat?

178
00:27:38,280 --> 00:27:42,160
I send a postcard to you saying
I love you and will keep our date today

179
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:43,080
A postcard?

180
00:27:43,440 --> 00:27:44,200
Yes, a silly one, with the Pope
on the reverse side

181
00:27:44,640 --> 00:27:45,160
