182
00:27:45,320 --> 00:27:47,040
After our last meeting, as usual
Haven't you got it?

183
00:27:47,160 --> 00:27:48,040
No, bye

184
00:28:12,080 --> 00:28:14,480
May I speak to Mr. Mariusz, please?
It's the right number, isn't it?

185
00:28:14,600 --> 00:28:17,360
Mariusz! For you again!

186
00:28:18,360 --> 00:28:19,200
Hallo

187
00:28:48,040 --> 00:28:50,200
It's me, so you're there?

188
00:28:50,400 --> 00:28:51,040
Yes

189
00:28:51,560 --> 00:28:52,760
I tried to reach you but the number
was engaged all the time...

190
00:28:53,760 --> 00:28:55,280
