00:41:39,120 --> 00:41:39,960
Roman

275
00:42:02,520 --> 00:42:04,040
Please take me in your arms

276
00:42:06,280 --> 00:42:07,800
Take me tightly

277
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:09,680
I can't

278
00:42:13,440 --> 00:42:14,520
Please

279
00:42:25,120 --> 00:42:26,160
Oh please do

280
00:42:29,360 --> 00:42:30,880
You're not going to walk out on me

281
00:42:31,760 --> 00:42:35,080
...just because I went to bed with...

282
00:42:35,560 --> 00:42:38,840
I didn't know... I know you well
enough but I never thought...

283
00:42:39,080 --> 00:42:40,680
I didn't know how much
I'd hurt you

284
00:42:40,800 --> 00:42:44,800
I have no right to be jealous
I can't demand it from you

285
00:42:45,360 --> 00:42:48,000
Of course you have the right

286
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:50,800
You were right about that
other thing, too

287
00:42:50,880 --> 00:42:52,240
Nothing should be left unsaid

288
00:42:52,360 --> 00:42:56,160
I'll never lie to you again
I don't want to hide behind a wardrobe

289
00:42:56,960 --> 00:42:58,080
I had an extra key made

290
00:42:59,040 --> 00:43:01,520
You won't ever have to

291
00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:06,440
We should have a child, adopt one
You were right

292
00:43:17,400 --> 00:43:19,840
We need a rest from each other

293
00:43:21,960 --> 00:43:23,200
Yes

294
00:43:24,520 --> 00:43:27,320
All right, take a holiday

295
00:43:28,520 --> 00:43:30,400
And I'll talk to some lawyer in the
meantime about that adoption

296
00:43:33,600 --> 00:43:34,520
No, I want you to go away

297
00:43:36,560 --> 00:43:38,080
I won't have that physicist...

298
00:43:40,880 --> 00:43:41,920
Good

299
00:44:03,440 --> 00:44:04,120
Not too short?

300
00:44:05,800 --> 00:44:06,680
They're my wife's

301
00:44:10,920 --> 00:44:13,120
Could you tell me...

302
00:44:18,600 --> 00:44:20,320
How much is a ticket to Melbourne?

303
00:44:22,640 --> 00:44:23,360
Go away

304
00:44:25,360 --> 00:44:28,800
I just wanted to ask how much
is a ticket to Melbourne

305
00:44:29,960 --> 00:44:30,720
Janusz

306
00:44:33,200 --> 00:44:34,360
This gentleman will tell you all

307
00:44:34,440 --> 00:44:35,840
you want to know,
Melbourne is his department

308
00:44:37,480 --> 00:44:38,040
What can I do for you?

309
00:44:50,920 --> 00:44:53,040
It takes longer if you want a boy,
and much shorter with a girl

310
00:44:53,160 --> 00:44:56,240
The lawyer was very nice
It would be fully confidential

311
00:44:56,840 --> 00:44:58,240
All right, but how long does it take?

312
00:44:58,600 --> 00:45:00,960
Well, several months with a girl
Everybody wants a boy

313
00:45:01,040 --> 00:45:03,800
You'd just have to provide
a certificate of sterility

314
00:45:03,960 --> 00:45:05,680
I might get it from Mikolaj

315
00:45:05,840 --> 00:45:07,600
Tell me, Roman
Is it what you really want?

316
00:45:08,320 --> 00:45:08,760
Yes

317
00:45:10,320 --> 00:45:11,680
Want me to phone you every day
from Zakopane?

318
00:45:12,080 --> 00:45:12,960
No, don't do it

319
00:45:13,640 --> 00:45:14,480
But you do trust me, don't you?

320
00:45:36,400 --> 00:45:37,360
How are you?

321
00:45:38,520 --> 00:45:39,480
I hate you

322
00:45:43,400 --> 00:45:44,680
Why, you agreed, didn't you?

323
00:45:44,840 --> 00:45:46,120
Yes... But I didn't want it

324
00:45:47,600 --> 00:45:48,960
Has anything happened?
What's wrong?

325
00:45:49,120 --> 00:45:51,520
Nothing yet, but I know I'm a
different person now

326
00:45:52,760 --> 00:45:53,560
What do you mean?

327
00:45:57,440 --> 00:46:00,200
I want to sing
And to have a large audience

328
00:47:53,360 --> 00:47:54,640
Hallo?

329
00:47:54,840 --> 00:47:56,800
Good evening

330
00:47:57,720 --> 00:48:00,280
I couldn't get a connection at an
earlier hour... Mariusz, please?

331
00:48:01,200 --> 00:48:02,120
He's away
Who's speaking, please?

332
00:48:02,480 --> 00:48:04,440
A friend from the university

333
00:48:04,800 --> 00:48:06,200
My son went away to Zakopane to ski

334
00:48:06,280 --> 00:48:07,680
Do you want me to give him
your message?

335
00:48:18,920 --> 00:48:23,200
The tickets for today are sold out

336
00:48:23,320 --> 00:48:26,160
The booking-office does not sell
tickets in advance for tomorrow

337
00:48:26,280 --> 00:48:29,440
It's open daily from
seven thirty a.m.

338
00:48:29,960 --> 00:48:32,160
Passengers are invited
to come back tomorrow

339
00:48:34,280 --> 00:48:35,720
Two for ten thirty

340
00:48:40,360 --> 00:48:42,560
What are you doing here?

341
00:48:45,600 --> 00:48:47,520
I was told you went
for a skiing holiday

342
00:48:48,480 --> 00:48:51,160
I thought, maybe you are
in Zakopane So I came here too

343
00:49:05,320 --> 00:49:08,320
I forgot

344
00:49:08,720 --> 00:49:09,440
Hold this a minute, I forgot

345
00:49:27,360 --> 00:49:27,880
Is this the hospital?

346
00:49:28,800 --> 00:49:29,920
Yes, may I help you?

347
00:49:30,760 --> 00:49:33,080
This is Hanna Nycz speaking from
Zakopane, is my husband there?

348
00:49:33,200 --> 00:49:35,600
No, Doctor Nycz isn't here today
He phoned he wasn't coming

349
00:49:35,720 --> 00:49:36,400
Yes

350
00:49:39,200 --> 00:49:43,360
Would you please do me a favour?
Should my husband phone the hospital,

351
00:49:43,920 --> 00:49:45,400
Please tell him
I'm leaving for Warsaw

352
00:49:45,480 --> 00:49:46,680
on the first train or
bus I manage to catch

353
00:49:46,840 --> 00:49:48,160
I'll be home in the evening
Will you tell him?

354
00:49:48,680 --> 00:49:49,560
Yes

355
00:49:50,880 --> 00:49:51,680
I'll tell him

356
00:49:51,760 --> 00:49:52,560
Thank you

357
00:49:56,280 --> 00:49:57,280
I'd like to make another call,
please

358
00:49:57,440 --> 00:49:59,120
It won't take long
It's a local call

359
00:50:09,200 --> 00:50:11,040
Right here, at the refilling station

360
00:50:14,720 --> 00:50:17,840
No, just what I needed
They're perfect

361
00:51:07,440 --> 00:51:10,400
Your ticket, please

362
00:51:10,720 --> 00:51:13,120
Put the skis in the luggage-carrier

363
00:51:13,320 --> 00:51:14,280
Your tickets, please
Your ticket, Madam

364
00:51:14,880 --> 00:51:16,760
I have no ticket
But I must get to Warsaw

365
00:53:20,920 --> 00:53:21,640
Roman...

366
00:54:05,280 --> 00:54:06,040
Yes... Where? I see

367
00:54:22,440 --> 00:54:23,200
Can you hear me?

368
00:54:25,280 --> 00:54:27,520
Your wife is not in that hotel
in Zakopane

369
00:54:28,880 --> 00:54:30,760
She left for Warsaw in the morning

370
00:55:00,000 --> 00:55:00,800
Thirty-two...

371
00:55:01,960 --> 00:55:04,920
fifty-six... thirty-six...

372
00:55:55,880 --> 00:55:56,640
Hanka darling

373
00:56:00,040 --> 00:56:00,920
You're all right

374
00:56:05,200 --> 00:56:07,160
Oh God, you're all right

375
00:56:09,240 --> 00:56:10,040
I am

